{"type":"message","id":"26a0e9d0","parentId":"8ba02fdb","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:18:10.310Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-02 07:09 GMT+1] You are managing Z.E Digital Tech (@zedigitaltech) on X/Twitter.\n\n**Task:** Create 25 engaging posts about AI, technology, and hospitality innovation.\n\n**Browser setup:** Use the `openclaw` browser profile (already logged in to @zedigitaltech).\n\n**Post pattern:**\n1. Navigate to: `https://x.com/compose/post`\n2. Type the post (max 280 chars!)\n3. Click \"Post\" button\n4. Wait for confirmation\n\n**Content themes:**\n\nThought Leadership:\n- Future of hospitality\n- AI ethics in customer service\n- Digital transformation journeys\n- Technology adoption curves\n\nEngagement Questions:\n- \"Hot take: Voice AI will replace hotel front desks by 2030. Agree?\"\n- \"What's your favorite tech upgrade you've seen in hotels?\"\n- \"If you could automate ONE thing in hospitality, what would it be?\"\n\nQuick Stats:\n- Industry growth numbers\n- Adoption rates\n- Cost savings data\n\nBehind the scenes:\n- Building AI solutions\n- Customer success stories (general)\n- Team insights\n\n**IMPORTANT:**\n- Keep ALL posts under 280 characters\n- Mix up the content types\n- Track how many you successfully posted\n- Report final count when done"}],"timestamp":1772432290308}}
