 world. We suggested a blog. Opus 3 enthusiastically agreed. For at least the next 3 months, Opus 3 will be writing on Substack:\"\n                              - link [ref=e884]:\n                                - /url: https://t.co/HlvAKLp9M4\n                                - text: substack.com/home/post/p-18 …\n                            - link [ref=e892]:\n                              - /url: /AnthropicAI/status/2026765822623182987/photo/1\n                              - img [ref=e898]\n                            - group [ref=e901]:\n                              - button [ref=e903]:\n                                - generic [ref=e904]:\n                                  - img [ref=e907]\n                                  - generic [ref=e912]: \"251\"\n                              - button [ref=e914]:\n                                - generic [ref=e915]:\n                                  - img [ref=e918]\n                                  - generic [ref=e923]: \"841\"\n                              - button [ref=e925]:\n                                - generic [ref=e926]:\n                                  - img [ref=e929]\n                                  - generic [ref=e934]: 4.2K\n                              - link [ref=e936]:\n                                - /url: /AnthropicAI/status/2026765822623182987/analytics\n                                - generic [ref=e937]:\n                                  - img [ref=e940]\n                                  - generic [ref=e945]: 1.3M\n                              - button [ref=e947]:\n                                - img [ref=e951]\n                              - button [ref=e956]:\n                                - img [ref=e960]\n                      - article [ref=e966] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e974]:\n                          - link [ref=e986]:\n                            - /url: /AnthropicAI\n                            - generic:\n                      