{"type":"message","id":"b494085c","parentId":"f48eadf3","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:22:28.036Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create a simple script approach. Instead of clicking and typing through the browser tool, I should use a more direct approach by using the exec tool to interact with the browser via AppleScript or similar automation. But first, let me try to use the browser tool in a more efficient way.\n\nActually, let me try a different approach. I'll use the browser tool to directly navigate to the compose page and then type in the text area. Let me try navigating to the compose post URL directly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me try a more efficient approach by using keyboard shortcuts to post. Let me navigate directly to the compose page:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3cb9c0e6ef794eef88bf0df0","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","profile":"openclaw","targetUrl":"https://x.com/compose/post"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zhipu","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":128,"output":156,"cacheRead":56832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57116,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772432538193}}
