{"type":"message","id":"f1fbe311","parentId":"a4144a90","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:22:46.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me now use a practical approach. I'll use Python with Selenium or Playwright through the exec tool to automate the posting process. This will be more reliable than trying to use the browser tool for complex interactions.\n\nLet me create a Python script that will:\n1. Connect to the existing Chrome browser\n2. Navigate to the compose page\n3. Create 25 posts with different content\n4. Track the success count\n\nFirst, let me check if playwright or selenium is available.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me use a more reliable approach with Python automation:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a2fba45958284187beacdc60","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which python3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zhipu","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":139,"output":122,"cacheRead":57152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57413,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772432557092}}
