{"type":"compaction","id":"69f63f31","parentId":"5024a23e","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:26:32.240Z","summary":"No prior history.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser requested creating 25 engaging X/Twitter posts for Z.E Digital Tech (@zedigitaltech) about AI, technology, and hospitality innovation. Posts should be max 280 characters, mix content types (thought leadership, engagement questions, stats, behind-the-scenes), and track successful posts.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Browser status confirmed running with `openclaw` profile (logged into @zedigitaltech)\n- Successfully navigated to `https://x.com/compose/post`\n- Encountered popup dialogs blocking access to compose area:\n  - \"Create a new List\" dialog - closed\n  - \"Do you want to follow @AnthropicAI?\" dialog - attempted to cancel\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- Target URL for posting: `https://x.com/compose/post`\n- Browser profile: `openclaw` (already authenticated)\n- Current targetId: `13D50928470BE49611BF928B36B4758C`\n- Page keeps redirecting/navigating away from compose page (to profile pages like @AnthropicAI, @GoogleDeepMind)\n- Need to get compose textbox visible and Post button enabled to begin creating 25 posts\n- Content themes prepared: Future of hospitality, AI ethics, digital transformation, engagement questions, industry stats, behind-the-scenes","firstKeptEntryId":"a5d8ebae","tokensBefore":60119,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":false}
